        com.unboundid.ldif.LDIFChangeRecord nextRecord()
                                        throws IOException,
                                               com.unboundid.ldif.LDIFException
        Read the next change record from the underlying input stream.
        Returns:
        The next change record or null if the end of the input stream has been reached.
        Throws:
        IOException - If there was an error reading from the input stream.
        com.unboundid.ldif.LDIFException - If there was an error parsing the data read from the input stream.
